<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Paused - Soda City Outdoors</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/styles.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: #f8fafc;
        }
        .paused-section {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .paused-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #ffc107;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            color: #856404;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="paused-section">
        <div class="paused-icon">⏸️</div>
        <h1 class="mb-4">Account Paused</h1>
        
        <div class="alert-box">
            <h4>Your account has been temporarily paused</h4>
            <p class="mb-0">Due to payment issues, your account access has been temporarily paused.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mb-4">
            <h5>How to resolve this:</h5>
            <ol class="text-start">
                <li>Update your payment information</li>
                <li>Resolve any outstanding payment issues</li>
                <li>Contact support if you need assistance</li>
                <li>Your account will be reactivated once payment is processed</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="d-grid gap-2">
            <a href="mailto:scoadmin@sodacityoutdoors.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i>Contact Support
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">
                Return to Homepage
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-4 text-muted">
            <small>
                <strong>Support Email:</strong> scoadmin@sodacityoutdoors.com<br>
                <strong>Response Time:</strong> Usually within 24 hours
            </small>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 